@startuml
participant "producer.js" as Producer
participant "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "consumer.js" as Consumer
participant "ml_consumer.js" as MLConsumer
participant "pre_process.js" as Preprocessor
participant "tf_model.js" as TFModel
participant "MongoDB" as MongoDB

Producer -> Kafka : Publish stock data
Kafka -> Consumer : Consume stock data
Consumer -> MongoDB : Update stock data

Kafka -> MLConsumer : Consume stock data
MLConsumer -> Preprocessor : Preprocess data
Preprocessor -> MLConsumer : Return preprocessed data
MLConsumer -> TFModel : Generate prediction
TFModel -> MLConsumer : Return prediction
MLConsumer -> MongoDB : Log prediction

@enduml